Cuban Chrome - Season 1, Episode 1


Stuck in a Time Warp

Automobile enthusiasts discuss classic cars from Cuba. In the series opener, a mechanic in Havana restores a '58 Chevy and a taxi driver searches the city for a part for his '53 Oldsmobile.
